BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260424T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260424T203000
DTSTAMP:20260420T233921
CREATED:20260212T142834Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260414T023026Z
UID:8189-1777053600-1777062600@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Cask & Still Social
DESCRIPTION:Be among the first to experience our Wheated Bourbon Mizunara Barrel Finish Reserve before the official release on Saturday\, May 9. \nAt the Cask & Still Social\, immerse yourself in the world of exceptional whiskey\, delectable food\, and engaging conversation with whiskey experts for $60. Enjoy a laid-back\, welcoming atmosphere as you connect with fellow enthusiasts and savor the rich flavors of Sweet Mash Whiskeys with signature cocktails and a curated selection of samples. \nThis 2.5-hour event will feature whiskey tasting stations\, passed appetizers\, and the opportunity to deepen your knowledge of the Hard Truth brand through expert-led discussions. Meet our brand ambassadors and talented staff who\, will guide you through each tasting experience\, providing insights into the artistry behind each whiskey expression. \nWhether you’re a connoisseur or new to whiskey\, this event promises an unforgettable evening. Limited spots are available — secure your place today!
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/cask-still-social-4/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260509T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260509T170000
DTSTAMP:20260420T233921
CREATED:20260105T185236Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260413T133114Z
UID:8143-1778313600-1778346000@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Hard Truth on the Rocks Opening Day!
DESCRIPTION:Join us Saturday\, May 9\, for opening weekend of the Hard Truth Terrace and the debut of Mizunara Finished Wheated Bourbon from our 2026 Barrel Finish Reserve collection. \nWe’ll be celebrating this rare release with cocktails\, guided tastings\, and seasonal food offerings in the open air. \nStarting at noon\, the terrace will welcome guests for: \n\nSpecialty cocktails\, guided tastings\, and bottle sales of Hard Truth Barrel Finish Reserve Straight Wheated Bourbon Finished on Mizunara\nSeasonal bites from the terrace bar\nOutdoor seating\nEvening live music\n\nWith warmer weather\, fresh flavors\, and a standout release\, terrace season starts here. \n 
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/hard-truth-on-the-rocks-opening-day-2/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260510T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260510T150000
DTSTAMP:20260420T233921
CREATED:20260312T170132Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T150921Z
UID:8281-1778407200-1778425200@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Mother's Day Brunch
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Mother’s Day at Hard Truth Distilling Co. with a relaxed\, open‑seating brunch experience in the House of Rye. Gather with family and friends and enjoy the rustic charm\, wooded surroundings\, and signature Hard Truth hospitality that make events here unforgettable.\nPair your meal with handcrafted cocktails or sips from the mimosa bar\, then enjoy a stroll through the distillery grounds as you continue your Mother’s Day celebration. \nMenu announcement coming soon. \nHandcrafted cocktails and mimosa bar will be available for additional purchase. \nBuffet is all ages; must be 21+ to purchase and consume alcohol. \nSeating is limited\, so make your reservation today.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/mothers-day-brunch-2/
END:VEVENT
