BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260530T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260530T210000
DTSTAMP:20260420T233921
CREATED:20260414T160055Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260414T160055Z
UID:8363-1780164000-1780174800@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Night 1
DESCRIPTION:ROUND 1: RUMBLE ON THE ROCKS \nIt’s on. The bands are locked in\, the stage is set\, and Round 1 of Rumble on the Rocks is bringing serious heat.\nCome out and experience a full night of live music as these bands battle it out for a shot at the finals—and a chance to win BIG:\n\n$2\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville$1\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n\nNIGHT ONE FEATURES: \n\nSlow Gin\nBuck Knawe & The Quick Draw\nZillafyde\nSweet Pea & The Pods\nHigh Street Jack\nWest Fork Revival**Order of performance is determined on the day of the event and may not match the above order**\n\nThis is a FAN-VOTED competition; your vote decides who moves on.\n\n\nVoting details:\nBallots are $10\nEach ballot = votes for TWO bands\nTop TWO bands advance to the finals\n\nExpect fast-paced sets\, quick transitions\, and nonstop energy from start to finish.\n\nPro tip: Come early\, stay loud\, and support your favorite bands—crowd turnout makes a difference.\nThis isn’t just a show… it’s a showdown.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/rumble-on-the-rocks-night-1/
END:VEVENT
