UID:8368-1781373600-1781384400@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Final Round
DESCRIPTION:It all comes down to this. \n\nThe top bands from Round 1 are back—two from Night One and two from Night Two—and they’re going head‑to‑head in the final showdown. \nWhat’s on the line: \n$2\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n$1\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville \nWinners are decided by YOU + the judges.\nFan votes and judges’ scores combine to crown the champions—and your vote truly counts. \nAdmission: $10\nYour $10 entry includes your official voting ballot\, so every ticket holder gets a say in who takes it all. \nExpect the best of the best: dialed‑in sets\, high stakes\, and a night that actually means something for these artists. \nBring your crew. Be loud. Cast your vote.\nFour bands. One stage. Two winners.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/rumble-on-the-rocks-finals/
END:VEVENT
